      "rendered": "@NonprofitOrgs to Report Live from the 2014 Cause Marketing Forum"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/Square-Graphic-Annoucement-Nonprofits-at-Cause-Marketing-Forum.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-16140\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Square Graphic Annoucement Nonprofits at Cause Marketing Forum\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/Square-Graphic-Annoucement-Nonprofits-at-Cause-Marketing-Forum-300x300.jpg?resize=300%2C300\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/Square-Graphic-Annoucement-Nonprofits-at-Cause-Marketing-Forum.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/Square-Graphic-Annoucement-Nonprofits-at-Cause-Marketing-Forum.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/Square-Graphic-Annoucement-Nonprofits-at-Cause-Marketing-Forum.jpg?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/Square-Graphic-Annoucement-Nonprofits-at-Cause-Marketing-Forum.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/Square-Graphic-Annoucement-Nonprofits-at-Cause-Marketing-Forum.jpg?w=500&amp;ssl=1 500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>Through a partnership with the\u00a0<a href=\"http://pir.org/\">Public Interest Registry</a>, <a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/heather-mansfield/\">Heather Mansfield</a> of Nonprofit Tech for Good will be attending the <a href=\"http://www.causemarketingforum.com/site/c.bkLUKcOTLkK4E/b.8340961/k.4050/2014_Conference.htm\">Cause Marketing Forum</a>\u00a0(<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23CMF2014\">#CMF2014</a>)\u00a0in Chicago on May 28 and May 29 to report live and\u00a0share the event in real-time with the\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/nonprofitorgs\">@NonprofitOrgs</a>\u00a0community. The objectives are:</p>\n<p><strong>1)</strong> To share with the nonprofit community who can not be in attendance the best advice and marketing tips provided by the\u00a0<a href=\"http://www.causemarketingforum.com/site/c.bkLUKcOTLkK4E/b.8906829/k.9603/CMF2014_Program.htm\">expert speakers</a>\u00a0at the forum.</p>\n<p><strong>2)</strong> To study how to report live effectively from a large scale, multiple day event using primarily\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/nonprofitorgs\">Twitter</a>,\u00a0<a href=\"http://instagram.com/nonprofitorgs\">Instagram</a>, <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nonprofitorgs\">Facebook</a>, and <a href=\"https://plus.google.com/+nonprofitorgs/posts\">Google+</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>3)</strong>\u00a0To help spread the news about the soon-to-be launched\u00a0<a href=\"http://globalngo.org/\">.NGO and .ONG domains</a>.</p>\n",
      "protected": false
    },
    "excerpt": {
      "rendered": "<p>Through a partnership with the\u00a0Public Interest Registry, Heather Mansfield of Nonprofit Tech for Good will be attending the Cause Marketing Forum\u00a0(#CMF2014)\u00a0in Chicago on May 28 and May 29 to report live and\u00a0share the event in real-time with the\u00a0@NonprofitOrgs\u00a0community. The objectives are: 1) To share with the nonprofit community who can not be in attendance the best advice and marketing tips provided by the\u00a0expert speakers\u00a0at the forum. 2) To study how to report live effectively from a large scale, multiple day event using primarily\u00a0Twitter,\u00a0Instagram, Facebook, and Google+. 3)\u00a0To help spread the news about the soon-to-be launched\u00a0.NGO and .ONG domains.</p>\n",
      "protected": false
    },
